		screen_text = "You seek to champion Princess Glamoulla's cause? I am not fully convinced she would make a good queen. Thought it's true our queen cowardly fled to Isle of Rhea Yhanity when our realm needed a defender, a role you have taken upon yourself. Allright, if one as trustworthy as you seeks to put Princess Glamoulla on the throne, I have no objections. Very well, the Isle of Rhea Yhanity is now open to you.";
	}
}
[conv_c24_r4_fairy_trees_asking_help_4_princess_next]
